### Test NBA 2025 Data Import - CSE Department Placement Records
### Make sure your Spring Boot application is running on localhost:8080

### 1. First, login as admin to get JWT token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@piemr.edu.in",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 2. Preview NBA 2025.xlsx file structure (use token from login response)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/validate/preview-nba2025
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 3. Check data processing status (use token from login response)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/data/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. Process NBA 2025 Excel data - CSE Batch 2018-2022 (use token from login response)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/data/process-nba2025
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Verify imported users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 6. Check CSE batch statistics for 2022
GET http://localhost:8080/api/batches/2022/CSE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. Search for specific students
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/search?query=18CS
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
